<section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 via-blue-50 to-pink-50" data-controller="static">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
      We're Building the
      <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        Future of E-commerce
      </span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      Our mission is to democratize online selling by making it incredibly simple for anyone to start and grow their online business.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- Story Section -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          e-dukaan was born from a simple observation: starting an online store shouldn't require a computer science degree. We watched countless entrepreneurs struggle with complex platforms, expensive developers, and technical barriers that stood between them and their dreams.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          In 2023, our team of passionate developers and entrepreneurs came together with a bold vision: what if we could reduce the time to launch an online store from weeks to seconds? What if we could make e-commerce accessible to everyone, regardless of their technical background?
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Today, e-dukaan powers over 50,000 online stores worldwide, helping entrepreneurs turn their ideas into thriving businesses with just a few clicks.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-secondary/10 rounded-3xl p-8">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-transparent">2023</div>
